---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SDub Media | Nashville Video Production">

<section class="hero">
  <span class="eyebrow">SDub Media &nbsp;·&nbsp; Nashville, TN</span>
  <h1><span class="accent">Recurring video</span> for businesses.<br>A few weddings a year.</h1>
  <p class="hero-subtitle">One team, obsessively consistent. We help businesses show up every week with content that actually gets made. And we still pick up a camera for eight weddings a year because we love it.</p>
  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="/business" class="btn btn-primary">For Businesses</a>
    <a href="/weddings" class="btn">For Weddings</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Trusted by</span>
      <h2>Clients who show up every week</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="logo-strip">
      <span class="brand">Coldwell Banker Southern Realty</span>
      <span class="brand">Webb School</span>
      <span class="brand">Elite Dance</span>
      <span class="brand">Nolensville Dance Company</span>
      <span class="brand">Tutoring Rocks</span>
      <span class="brand">Middle of the Story Podcast</span>
      <span class="brand">Ballet Ball Nashville</span>
      <span class="brand" style="opacity: 0.6;">Tone Films</span>
      <span class="brand" style="opacity: 0.6;">Lighthouse Media</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background: var(--soft);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2>Pick the door that fits.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="two-door">
      <a href="/business" class="door">
        <img class="door-photo" src="/images/home/business.png" alt="A video crew filming a business owner on camera in a Nashville office" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
        <div class="door-content">
          <h3>Business</h3>
          <p>Weekly content series, corporate podcasts, agent-on-camera reels, headshot days, branded events. Retainer-friendly.</p>
          <span class="door-arrow">See what we do for businesses →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/weddings" class="door">
        <img class="door-photo" src="/images/home/weddings.png" alt="A videographer filming a couple at golden hour at a Tennessee wedding venue" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
        <div class="door-content">
          <h3>Weddings &amp; Portraits</h3>
          <p>Cinematic wedding films, family sessions, and senior portraits. Limited bookings each year. Nashville, destination, or wherever you're celebrating.</p>
          <span class="door-arrow">Check availability →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">What we do</span>
      <h2>Built for the week ahead. And the one after that.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="tiles">
      <div class="tile">
        <img class="tile-image" src="/images/home/recurring.png" alt="A crew filming a weekly branded content shoot in a studio" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
        <h3>Recurring Content</h3>
        <p>Your brand needs to show up. Not once. Every single week. We build production rhythms around your calendar (batch shoots, fast edits, consistent style) so your content pipeline never stalls.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tile">
        <img class="tile-image" src="/images/home/podcast.png" alt="A multi-camera podcast studio with two people at microphones" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
        <h3>Podcast Production</h3>
        <p>Multi-camera. Studio or on-location. Every episode delivered with full edit, social cutdowns, and platform-ready exports. One session, every format your audience watches on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tile">
        <img class="tile-image" src="/images/home/events.png" alt="Studio lighting and a camera set up for headshots at a company event" loading="lazy" width="1536" height="1024" />
        <h3>Events &amp; Headshots</h3>
        <p>The annual gala. The quarterly headshot refresh. The training day nobody planned for. We bring the crew, the gear, and the turnaround, so the moment actually gets used.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container-narrow text-center">
    <span class="eyebrow">The difference</span>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Great content isn't a moment.<br>It's a system.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-dim);">One video won't change your business. Fifty will. We design production systems that run month after month (same quality, same schedule, zero hand-holding) so your brand stays visible without your team managing it.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <a href="/business" class="btn">See how it works</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container-narrow text-center">
    <span class="eyebrow">Say hi</span>
    <h2>Let's talk about what you're planning.</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 520px; margin: 1.5rem auto 2rem;">Whether it's a weekly series for your brand or a single wedding day, start with a message and we'll reply within 24 hours.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
